> BLACKARACHNIA was quite fine with letting the bug rot to his own ends, and
> at this point she went to vanish over to the underbrush, intent on headnig
> elsewhere if not noticed, her cloak powered up.
>
> WASPINATOR let out an 'EEP', and quickly pointed, "Over there, there,
> zerrre!"  His mandibles gesticulating over towards the ground!

The three Dinosaur styled PREDACONS walked over to WASPINATOR, each of
them well known associates of MAGMATRON, companions from when he first
went into the cosmos to begin his days of conquering.

GUILEDART, his right hand mech, KILLERPUNCH, who was his best
interrogation and intelligence officer and BAZOOKA, the honorable
soldier. All them powerful in their own right, and yet here they were
all together looking at WASPINATOR.

"I watched the tapes." KILLER PUNCH said. "Hydras was taken by
Cyclonus, Scourge amd some seekers." He said to GUILEDART.

Nodding GUILEDART also looked at WASPINATOR but spoke to KILLER PUNCH,
"Perhaps he doesn't know either."

"Tell us insect what you know!" BAZOOKA said, "Or we will squash you
like a bug."
